## Why This Project Matters
This project demonstrates:
- End-to-end data pipeline design
- Time series forecasting with ARIMA
- Interactive visualization with Dash
- Handling diverse data sources (stocks, commodities, index, crypto)

It is an ideal portfolio project to showcase skills in **data engineering, analytics, and visualization**.